This paper discusses challenges in the medical image analysis field, which involves computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG) techniques. The paper also touches upon considerations related to human-computer interaction (cs.HC) and information retrieval (cs.IR).
